 Tiong-kok Tong5-tiau5 e5 si5, u7 chit8 e5 tai7-sin5 siN3 Poe5 mia5 Tou7, in-ui7 hong kong-chiok ti7 Chin3 e5 sou2-chai7, sou2-i2 lang5 kong2 Poe5 Chin3-kong. U7 chit8 jit8 hut-jian5 lang5 lai5 po3 i kong2, Li2 e5 in3 phah-m7-kiN3 lah. PiN-a2 e5 lang5 thiaN-kiN3 an2-ni, tai7-ke toa7 kiaN, bin7 long2 sit-sek. (Kou2-cha2 choe3 koaN e5 lang5 in3 na7 phah-m7-kiN3, koaN liau2 boe7 soah tit, u7 si5 oe7 u7 choe7). Tok8-tok8 Chin3-kong long2 bo5 sim2-mih8 khoa3-i3, iu5-goan5 kio3 lang5 pi7-pan7 ian5-siah8 lai5 chhiaN2 lang5-kheh, hoaN-hoaN hi2-hi2, long2 bo5 hoan5-lo2. Cheng3-lang5 m7 chai i e5 i3-su3, put-chi2 ki5-koai3. Kau3 poaN3-mi5 e5 si5, hut-jian5 u7 lang5 lai5 ka7 i kong2, In3 koh ti7-teh lah. Chin3-kong ia7 bo5 hoaN-hi2 e5 khoan2. Au7-lai5 u7 lang5 mng7 i kong2, An3-chaiN2-iuN7 li2 thai3 an2-ni? Chin3-kong chiah kong2, Che in3 put-ko3 si7 ge5-iah8 thau-theh8 khi3 eng7 chit8-e7; khoaN-khoaN-si7 chu7-jian5 ka-ki7 koh theh8-lai5 he7-teh; na7-si7 chhiN-kong5 chhe7, pek siuN kin2, kiaN-liau2 thau-theh8 in3 e5 lang5 bo5 hoat-tou7 thang theh8 to3-tng2-lai5, tek-khak chiong in3 hiat loh8 chui2-nih8, a2-si7 he2-nih8 sio; (in-ui7 thau-theh8 in3 e5 lang5 si7 si2 choe7); an2-ni chiu7 bo5 hoat-tou7 thang chhe7 liau2. 
 Teng2-bin7 chit chat e5 kou3-su7, m7 si7 kah lang5 hoan7-su7 pang3 bo5-iau3 bo5-kin2, si7 kong2 bo5-lun7 tu2-tioh8 sim2-mih8 kin2-kip e5 tai7-chi3, long2 tioh8 sim-koaN liah8-tiaN7, phah-sng3 hou7 ho2, m7-thang pak-lai7 ju5 chhiang2-chhiang2, chhiN-kong5 tit8-tit8 pek, chiu7 bo5 iau3-kin2 e5 tai7-chi3, ia7 long2-chhut chin toa7 e5 su7 lai5. U7 si5 ko3-jin5 e5 tai7-chi3, pek kau3 chu7-chin7; ia7 na7 khah thoan5-the2 e5 su7, chiu7 pek kau3 piN3 chiaN5 hoan2-poan7 e5 toa7 choe7. Siong5-siong5 bat khoaN3 lang5 ka-ki7 phaiN2 ki3-ti5, mih8 siu-liau2 boe7 ki3 tit, lam7-sam2 bu5-loa7 lang5, hai7 lang5 khi3 siu7 chin choe7 e5 kan-khou2; kau3 au7-lai5 koh chhe7 tioh8, i ia7 m7 jin7 ka-ki7 m7 tioh8, hoan2-tng2 gi5 si7 hit e5 lang5 theh8-lai5 chhang3-teh heng5 i. Siok8-gu2 kong2, Kin2-su7 khoaN pan7; kho2-kian3 seng3-te7 siuN-kip e5 lang5, kai3 gau5 long3-phoa3 tai7-chi3. 
 Chin2-che3 lang5 tioh8 kip8-si5 
 Chong Chiu kek8 song3-hiong e5 si5-chun7, khi3 kiN3 Kam Ho5-hou5, kiu5 beh ka7 i chioh tam7-poh8 bi2-niu5. Kam Ho5-hou5 kong2, ChhiaN2 theng3-hau7 teh, koh keh bo5 kui2 jit8, goa2 beh tit-tioh8 chit8 e5 khah ho2 toe7-hng e5 kheh, goa2 chiah saN pah e5 gun5 chioh li2; an2-ni ho2 m7? Chong Chiu thiaN-liau2 m7 hoaN-hi2, chiu7 siat chit8 e5 phi3-ju7 kong2, Goa2 cha7-jit8 lai5 e5 si5, ti7 lou7-nih8 u7 thiaN-kiN3 teh au5-kio3 e5 siaN-im, goa2 chiu7 si3-koe3 khoaN3, khoaN3 to bo5 lang5, goan5-lai5 si7 ti7 chhia-lou7-kau nih8, u7 chit8 be2 chit-a2-hi5 teh au5-kio3. Goa2 chiu7 mng7 i kong2, Li2 an3-chaiN2-iuN7 thai3 lai5 tiam3 chia? Kio3 goa2 beh sim2-mih8 su7? Hit e5 chit-a2-hi5 kong2, Goa2 si7 tang-hai2 e5 pho2-sin5, li2 kheng2 eng7 chit8 chin chui2, a2-si7 chit8 tau2 chui2, lai5 kiu3 goa2 e5 oah8-mia7 bo5? Goa2 chiu7 ka7 i kong2, ChhiaN2 theng3-hau7 teh, goa2 beh loh8 lam5 khi3 kiaN5-iu5, chiah khng3 Gou5 Oat8 nng7 kok e5 ong5, chiong se-kang e5 chui2 khui hou7 thau3 lai5, thang ngia5-chih li2 to3-khi3 hai2-nih2, an2-ni ho2 m7? Hit chiah chit-a2-hi5 siu7-khi3 kong2, Goa2 put-ko3 chit8 si5 chhau3-khiau2 tu2-tioh8 chit ho7 e5 kan-lan5, chi2-u7 beh kiu5 chit8 chin a2-si7 chit8 tau2 e5 chui2, chit8 tiau5 mia7 chiu7 oe7 oah8; na7 chiau3 li2 kong2, put-ju5 khi3 koe-chhi7-nih8 e5 hi5-pou2 tiam3, khoaN3 goa2 chiu7 ho2. 
 TaN lun7-kau3 hian7-si5 e5 song3-hiong lang5, ia7 chin choe7 long2 boe7 sng3 tit. Hit tiong-kan u7 koa2 si7 in-ui7 phiau5, tou2, im2 lai5 ti3-kau3 an2-ni, sng3 si7 chu7-chok chu7-siu7, che m7 bian2 kong2; ia7 u7 koa2 si7 tai3-chit8, khe5-kha, phoa3-siuN3, thai2-ko, chhiN-mi5, a2-si7 kou-khou2 e5 lau7-lang5, in-ui7 put-heng7 lai5 ti3-kau3 an2-ni. U7 koa2 hou7 Chu5-hui7-iN7 siu-iong5 khi3; m7 ku2 iau2 chin-choe7, koaN-hu2 chiau3-kou3 thai3 oe7 chiau5 tioh8? An2-ni tek-khak tioh8 kho3 chiah-e5 u7 chiN5 e5 lang5, chiau3 in e5 lek8-liong7, than3 hit e5 si5-ki lai5 pang-chan7 in, hou7 in chek-siau2 seng5 to, oe7 tang3 tou7 jit8. Na7 beh phah-ka-lauh8 chit8-liap8 png7-liap8, kong3-si2 saN chiah kau2. Tng lang5 bin7-cheng5 kong2, Si7 goa2 theh8 boe7 khi2; na7 bo5, goa2 to kam-goan7 choe3 ho2 su7; an2-ni kiam2 m7 si7 kap teng2-bin7 hit e5 kou3-su7 sio-siang7 mah? Seng3-keng Ma2-thai3 25 chiuN 42-45 chat kong2, In-ui7 goa2 iau, lin2 m7-bat hou7 goa2 chiah8; goa2 chhui3-ta, lin2 m7-bat hou7 goa2 lim; goa2 chhut-goa7, lin2 m7-bat hou7 goa2 toa3, goa2 thng3-pak-theh, lin2 m7-bat hou7 goa2 chheng7; goa2 phoa3-piN7 kap ti7 kaN-nih8, lin2 m7-bat khoaN3-kou3 goa2. In ia7 beh in3 kong2, Chu2 ah, goan2 sim2-mih8 si5 khoaN3-kiN3 li2 iau, a2-si7 chhui3-ta, a2-si chhut-goa7, a2-si7 thng3-pak-theh, a2-si7 phoa3-piN7, a2-si7 ti7 kaN-nih8, lai5 bo5 hok8-sai7 li2 ah? I chiu7 beh in3 i kong2, Goa2 sit8-chai7 ka7 lin2 kong2, Lin2-ki3-jian5 bo5 kiaN5 i ti7 chiah-e5 chi3-bi5 soe3-e5 e5 chit8 e5, chiu7-si7 bo5 kiaN5 i ti7 goa2. 
 Ho7 hok oh-tit hun-piat 
 Tiong-kok e5 pak-hng, oa2-kun7 goa7-kok e5 pian-kai3, mia5 kio3 Sai3-chiuN7. Ti7 kou2-cha2 e5 si5, hit sou2-chai7 u7 chit8 e5 lau7-lang5, in tau chhi7 chit8 chiah be2, bo5 tiuN-ti5 soa3 phah-m7-kiN3, tai7-khai3 si7 chau2 tui3 pak-peng5 Ou5-jin5 e5 toe7-hng khi3. Lang5 chiu7 lai5 tham3 i, soa3 ka7 i an-ui3. Hit e5 lau7-lang5 kong2, Chit e5 tai7-chi3 bo5 tek-khak; si7 hok-khi3 ia7 kaN2. Ke3 bo5 kui2 geh8 jit8, hit chiah sit-loh8 khi3 e5 be2, hut-jian5 chham chit8 chiah Ou5 jin5 e5 be2 saN-kap to3-lai5. Lang5 chiu7 long2 lai5 khoaN3, ia7 soa3 ka7 i kiong-hi2. Hit e5 lau7-lang5 kong2, Chit e5 tai7-chi3 bo5 tek-khak; si7 chai-e7 ia7 kaN2. Au7-lai5 i e5 kiaN2 siong5-siong5 ai3 khia5 hit chiah be2; u7 chit8 jit8 m7 tu2 ho2 khi3 hou7 poah8-loh8-lai5, kha-kut soa3 siang3 tng7-khi3. Cheng3 lang5 iu7 lai5 tham3-bai7 i, soa3 ka7 i an-ui3. Hit e5 lau7-lang5 kong2, Chit ho7 tai7-chi3 bo5 tek-khak; si7 hok-khi3 ia7 kaN2. Koh keh chiaN5 ni5 ku2, Ou5-jin5 nia2 chin choe7 peng, kong-phah jip8 Sai3-chiuN7, kiN3-na7 siau3-lian5 lang5 long2 tioh8 kiah8 ke-si khi3 kap Ou5-jin5 saN-thai5. Tng hit-si5 Sai3-chiuN7 e5 lang5, chap8 hun7 si2 kau2 hun7 khah ke khi3. Chi2-u7 chit e5 pai2-kha e5 in pe7 kiaN2 tit-tioh8 po2-choan5 in e5 siN3-mia7. 
 Chiau3 teng2-bin7 e5 khoan2 ka7 i khoaN3, lang5 ti7 chit se3-kan, tit-tioh8 hok-khi3, ia7 m7-bian2 hoaN-hi2, tu2-tioh8 chai-e7, ia7 m7-bian2 hoan5-lo2 : tioh8 ai3 chai hok-khi3 e5 lai7-bin7, ia7 u7 chai-e7, chai-e7 e5 tiong-kan, iu5-goan5 u7 hok-khi3. Lang5 na7 oe7 beng5-pek8 chit e5 to7-li2, chiu7 put-lun7 ti7 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7, ti7 sim2-mih8 si5, sim-koaN bo5 m7 peng5-an khoai3-lok8. 
 Tui3 sio2-khoa2 oe7 chai toa7 hang7 
 Tiu7-ong5 u7 chit8 jit8 tit-tioh8 chit8 siang chhiuN7-ge5 e5 ti7, i e5 jin5-sin5 Ki5 Chu2 khoaN3-liau2 put-chi2 iu-bun7 kiaN-hiaN5. Lang5 mng7 i kong2, Che sng3 bo5 sim2-mih8 iau3-kin2 e5 su7, an3-chaiN2-iuN7 li2 ia7 kiaN kau3 an2-ni? Ki5 Chu2 chiah kong2, In-ui7 lang5 na7 u7 chit ho7 ge5-ti7, chiu7 m7 koh eng7 chhou-hui5 e5 chiu2-poe, tek-khak tioh8 eng7 gek8-poe lai5 phoe3 i. Kau3 u7 ge5-ti7 gek8-poe, chiu7 m7 koh chiah8 hit ho7 chhou-chhai3 pian7-png7 lah; tek-khak oe7 beh chiah8 hiah-e5 san-tin hai2-bi7. Na7 chiah8 san-tin hai2-bi7, chiu7 m7 kheng2 koh chheng7 chit ho7 chhou-pou3 i-chiuN5, tioh8 hit ho7 leng5-lo5 phang2-si tiu5-toan7 chiah beh chheng7. Na7 kau3 chiah8 chheng7 hiah ho2, chiu7 m7 kheng2 koh khia7 chit ho7 m7 chiaN5 chhu3, tek-khak tioh8 khia7 koaiN5 lau5 toa7 chhu3; an2-ni na2 khi3 na2 chhia-hoa5, m7 chai beh kau3 toh-loh8 ui5 chi2. Au7-lai5 Tiu7-ong5 ko2-jian5 chin chhia-chhi2, long2 bo5 chiau3-kou3 peh-siN3, ti3-kau3 hou7 Chiu Bu2-ong5 biat8-khi3. 
 Kou2 lang5 gian5 kong2, Ai3 chheng7 e5 ai3 io5, ai3 chiah8 e5 ai3 phiau5. In-ui7 u7 lang5 ia7 khioh siok8-gu2 khi2-lai5 kong2, Sin-nih8 bo5 i, pi7 lang5 khi, khiok ia7 u7 iaN2; bo5 lun7 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7, long2 si7 an2-ni. Sou2-i2 tai7-ke na2 tau3 na2 chhia-hoa5. Ki5-sit8 lan2 lang5 teh khia7-khi2 e5 sou2-chai7, kap chiah8 chheng7 e5 su7, chi3-ho2 si7 tioh8 choe5-chaN2 chheng-khi3 choe3 iau3-kin2; chhian-ban7 m7-thang him-sian7 pat8 lang5 e5 hoan5-hoa. In-ui7 na7 u7 chit khoan2 e5 ho2 mih8, tek-khak tioh8 chhe7 pat8 hang7 ho2 mih8 lai5 phoe3 i; na7 bo5, to thin7 boe7 ke3. Chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 beng5 khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 lang5, ui7-tioh8 chian2-hoat, ia7 te3 lang5 choe3 chit8 su poaN3-le2-hok8, khiok ia7 u7 bo7-a2, m7-ku2 iau2 khiam3 chit8 siang ho2 e5 phe5-oe5; kau3 chiaN geh8 e5 chhoe it, tai7-ke teh chng, chong2-si7 i iau2 khiam3 chit8 hang7 chiu7 boe7 eng7 tit, khah kan-khou2 ia7 tioh8 boe2 lai5 thiN. Sou2-i2 u7 khun5-khiam7 ho2-tek e5 lang5, tek-khak tioh8 tui3 sio2-khoa2 e5 su7 lai5 jin7-chin. 
 Chhe7 boe7 si2 e5 hong-hoat 
