 Tong-si5 ia7 u7 chit8 e5 lang5, mia5 kio3 Che5 Chu2, ia7 beh oh8 chit ho7 boe7 si2 e5 hong-hoat; thiaN-kiN3 hit e5 lang5 si2, chiu7 put-chi2 iu-bun7 hoan5-lo2. Hu5 Chu2 thiaN-kiN3 chiu7 thi2-chhio3 i kong2, Li2 beh oh8 boe7 si2 e5 hong-hoat, iah8 hit e5 beh ka3 li2 e5 sian-siN i2-keng to si2-khi3 lah, li2 iau2-ku2 teh thoe3 i iu-bun7, m7 chai li2 si7 beh oh8 i sim2-mih8 leh? 
 TaN hian7-si5 e5 lang5 sou2 teh hok8-sai7 it-khai3 e5 ngou2-siong7, ia7 kong2 si7 kou2-cha2 e5 tiong-sin5 hau3-chu2; chhin-chhiuN7 TiuN Sun5 choe3 Tou-thian Tai7-te3, TiuN Gi5 choe3 Giok8-hong5 Tai7-te3, Li JiN2 choe3 Thai3-siong7 Lo2-kun, Lau5 Tiong5-seng choe3 Chin-bu2 Tai7-te3, Tan5 Chu2-chhun choe3 Bun5-chhiong Te3-kun, Tio7 Kong-beng5 choe3 Chai5-sin5 Phou5-sat, Lim5 Bek8-a2-che2 choe3 Thian-siong7 Seng3-bu2, Koan U2 choe3 Hiap8-thian Tai7-te3, TiuN To7-leng5 choe3 Thian-su, Sek-khia-bou5-ni5 choe3 Put8-chou2; chhin-chhiuN7 chiah-e5 kong2 boe7 tit liau2, m7 bian2 kong2 he si7 thou5-chhiok8 chha5 khek e5, bo5-leng5 bo5-siaN3, chiu7-si7 siat-su2 ko2-jian5 in hiah-e5 lang5 long2 iau2 ti7 se3-kan, in ia7 boe7 oe7 siuN2-su3 lang5 e5 siN-si2 ho7-hok, in-ui7 in ka-ki7 e5 siN-si2 ho7-hok, siong7-chhiaN2 boe7 oe7 ka-ki7 choe3 chu2 tit, beh thai3 oe7 koan2 lang5 e5 siN-si2 ho7-hok leh? Ho5-hong3 in i2-keng si2-khi3 kang2 chheng ni5 ku2, lian5-to7 si2-liau2 koh khah u7 chai5-leng5 pun2-su7 mah? Tek-khak bo5 chit tiau5 li2, tek-khak bo5 chit tiau5 li2. 
